                     <interp inst="t17811205-42-person502" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                  </persName>
             was sworn (she was not put upon her defence). That she was his sister's daughter, that he got her cloathed in Kirby-street, and bid her go home; said they offered to make it up with him for 3 l.</p>
